{"tid":2048772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會員劉穎鏇 支持記者影示威者大頭相,內有其可疑帳戶紀錄","createTime":"2020-06-03T04:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T06:51:02.000Z","uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4be8b80806342da742ea7ac4436fdb0f5a9d8a4b","tid":2048772,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2048604/page/8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2048604/page/8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/760</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDgZAMh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDgZAMh.png&h=3edbdeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1)條友竟然話支持香港記者影示威者大頭<br />\n記者報導絕對可以影示威現場<br />\n<ins>但影大頭零新聞價值,市民有需要你zoom埋去影示威者有無暗瘡?</ins><br />\n<ins>更唔好講香港警暴震動各國政界, 香港記者故意影大頭等同配合納粹暴行</ins><br />\n<br />\n2)而條友把唔認同香港記者呢種行為 撈埋藍絲屌記者黑記講<br />\n明顯就係大陸五毛的老屈手法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3)點解#760會員編號可以零記錄<br />\n呢類通常係打手公司大量註銷的假帳號,機手等有JOB再係電腦記錄搵番開工</span>"},{"pid":"245e18b4c7f5f061f2b513ed49f5f0ec97a94b44","tid":2048772,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"大量註<strong>冊</strong>的假帳號<br />\n<br />\n真係幾奇怪下"},{"pid":"bd873681d6b83fea1e2abcb4c860b7879cd0d6a0","tid":2048772,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}